{"tw": {"1517850": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Quickie: A Love Hotel Story", "steam_appid": 1517850, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/3ba95ab11d81e84271fb3b6b08a0099d.avif?t=1760590837\" width=622 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>快捷情趣酒店</strong></i>是一段關於愛與欲望的故事 ♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲透過八段不同的戀情主線，為你講述充滿浪漫與激情的邂逅。每段故事都融合了濃濃情感與香艷畫面，由手繪美術精心呈現，並搭配細緻入微的動畫演出，打造沉浸式的戀愛體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>那麼…你會選擇哪一段戀情走到最後？</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/648e8cedb866d856c97fce2eabfa5685.avif?t=1760590837\" width=610 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/126432f3b927e47715051c0fb7ebb75c.poster.avif?t=1760590837\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/126432f3b927e47715051c0fb7ebb75c.webm?t=1760590837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/126432f3b927e47715051c0fb7ebb75c.mp4?t=1760590837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲受女神異聞錄系列啟發，採用線性視覺小說形式，帶你逐一邂逅八位性格各異、外貌出眾的女性。深入她們的生活，了解她們的故事與掙扎，與她們在浪漫中逐漸走近…但最終，你只能選擇一位共度餘生…你會選誰？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/243d8254b322cdb3b504f036765f9123.avif?t=1760590837\" width=609 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/a0c5fe997a7406c218d2e7bd189999f9.poster.avif?t=1760590837\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/a0c5fe997a7406c218d2e7bd189999f9.webm?t=1760590837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/a0c5fe997a7406c218d2e7bd189999f9.mp4?t=1760590837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在精美流暢的H動畫中，配合嬌喘呻吟與撩人音效，為你帶來難以忘懷的感官盛宴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/d1ba6f9a824818ad66ba63b410f9674b.avif?t=1760590837\" width=610 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/7b3abd0e0711dcbe7b93b8c71bf72a06.poster.avif?t=1760590837\" width=800 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/7b3abd0e0711dcbe7b93b8c71bf72a06.webm?t=1760590837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517850/extras/7b3abd0e0711dcbe7b93b8c71bf72a06.mp4?t=1760590837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造、升級並自由裝修你的情趣酒店，提升酒店星級，打造你的東京愛情帝國！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >